diverse medical examination and treatment of people, maintaining the brand name hospital Tu Du; To well perform the task of professional support and technical transfer for grassroots medical establishments; improve the income and stabilize the life for civil servants - staff of the hospital ... That is the important premise to help doctors CKII. Pham Viet Thanh - People\'s Doctor, Director of Tu Du Hospital was honored to be one of the 18 most advanced models of Ho Chi Minh City, voted by the Council of Emulation and Commendation of the thousands of cadres and employees. the health care sector of nearly 100 units, medical facilities and pharmaceutical companies - in public and private medical equipment in the city.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>[:]', 'TS. BS. Phạm Việt Thanh', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '192-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-01-06 15:49:21', '2019-01-06 15:49:21', '', 192, 'http://localhost/2018/freelancer/BE/healthcare/192-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
